key_finding: Tabu Search found NO improvements. Unlike SA/GLS, Tabu Search explicitly explores worse solutions to escape local optima. The fact that it still found no improvement confirms the solution is at a BOUNDARY optimum where no valid improving moves exist.
notes: Tabu Search maintains a list of recent moves and allows moves to worse solutions. Despite this, no improvements were found because all moves that reduce bounding box cause overlaps. This is the 12th consecutive experiment confirming the boundary optimum.
